{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2016/05/27/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"AllThingsSmitty/css-protips","categoryHTML":"<h2>Translations</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/AllThingsSmitty/css-protips/tree/master/translations/pt-BR\">Português do Brasil</a></li>","updatedAt":"2016-05-27T21:53:03.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"caesar0301/awesome-pcaptools","categoryHTML":"<h2>Traffic Analysis/Inspection</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/seladb/PcapPlusPlus\">PcapPlusPlus</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/seladb/PcapPlusPlus\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.4k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1377,\"repo\":\"seladb/PcapPlusPlus\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->: PcapPlusPlus a multiplatform C++ network sniffing and packet parsing and manipulation framework. It's meant to be lightweight, efficient and easy to use. It's a C++ wrapper for popular engines like libpcap, WinPcap, DPDK and PF_RING. It also contains parsing and edit capabilities for many protocols including Ethernet, IPv4, IPv6, ARP, VLAN, MPLS, PPPoE, GRE, TCP, UDP, ICMP, DNS as well as layer 7 protocols like HTTP and SSL/TLS</li>","updatedAt":"2016-05-27T20:52:52.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"kjw0612/awesome-deep-vision","categoryHTML":"<h2>Papers</h2><h3>Understanding CNN</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Alexey Dosovitskiy, Thomas Brox,